query:
SELECT
            COUNT(*) as total_requests,
            COALESCE(SUM(total_tokens), 0)::bigint as total_tokens,
            SUM(total_cost)::float8 as total_cost
        FROM http_analytics
        WHERE uri LIKE '/ai/%'
            AND model = $1
            AND timestamp >= $2
            AND timestamp <= $3
            AND user_id IS NOT NULL
            AND user_email IS NOT NULL
